# Operations View & Audit Log - Implementation Guide

## Overview

This document describes the **Operations View** components that satisfy the "Memory & Feedback Moat" business requirement:

1. **Audit Log Viewer** - Tamper-evident log of all AI agent actions, human approvals, and system events
2. **Cron Job Manager** - Visual management interface for scheduled tasks (Phase 2: read-only, Phase 3: full control)

---

## Business Requirement: Memory & Feedback Moat

> **Requirement:** Build a compliant, tamper-evident log viewer and visual Cron Job manager to create an auditable trail of all AI decisions and human interventions.

### Why This Matters

1. **Compliance** - 36-month minimum data retention for regulatory requirements
2. **Trust** - Transparent AI reasoning visible to human reviewers
3. **Accountability** - Clear audit trail of who approved what and when
4. **Learning** - Historical data for improving AI decision-making
5. **Moat** - Proprietary operational data becomes competitive advantage

