## Security Considerations

1. **Access Control** - Only authorized users can view audit logs
2. **Rate Limiting** - Prevent abuse of query endpoints
3. **Input Validation** - All inputs validated with Zod schemas
4. **Hash Protection** - Store hashes in separate, read-only table
5. **Audit the Auditors** - Log all access to audit log viewer
